  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arch Legends is a classic third-person RPG with real-time combat! Powerful beings are emerging, and the Kingdom of Evereska is counting on you to exterminate the forces of darkness. Do you have what it takes to restore order to the world? Summon allies or trade on the global black market between players to help restore peace and order to the Kingdom! Arch Legends mixes classic RPG heritage with other innovative mechanics, creating an RPG experience like no other!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game will bring several adventures as if it had a gamemaster narrating classic RPG campaigns from which the player will benefit from new content, in addition to all this, it will have season passes COMPLETELY FREE.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>No micro-transactions! No cash shop!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The fights are intense and strategic and any mistake can make you lose.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/c37d751fa7192654eaf9b359c3f1113d.poster.avif?t=1731027657\" width=600 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/c37d751fa7192654eaf9b359c3f1113d.webm?t=1731027657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/c37d751fa7192654eaf9b359c3f1113d.mp4?t=1731027657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Players can choose from a variety of vocations and abilities, each with their own strengths and weaknesses!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/26762365c533b990af55e27ed83007e3.poster.avif?t=1731027657\" width=600 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/26762365c533b990af55e27ed83007e3.webm?t=1731027657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/26762365c533b990af55e27ed83007e3.mp4?t=1731027657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Players can summon allies who will help them face greater challenges and receive great rewards!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/fb3ad49dc7e3f0cbdf3dfe650c4387d5.poster.avif?t=1731027657\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/fb3ad49dc7e3f0cbdf3dfe650c4387d5.webm?t=1731027657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/fb3ad49dc7e3f0cbdf3dfe650c4387d5.mp4?t=1731027657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Players can join a guild and carry out special quests, evolving and receiving unique rewards to exchange for special items!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/ada1da6a7a817fdec98ea236780cf730.poster.avif?t=1731027657\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/ada1da6a7a817fdec98ea236780cf730.webm?t=1731027657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/ada1da6a7a817fdec98ea236780cf730.mp4?t=1731027657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arch Legends is a classic third-person RPG with real-time combat! Powerful beings are emerging, and the Kingdom of Evereska is counting on you to exterminate the forces of darkness. Do you have what it takes to restore order to the world? Summon allies or trade on the global black market between players to help restore peace and order to the Kingdom! Arch Legends mixes classic RPG heritage with other innovative mechanics, creating an RPG experience like no other!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game will bring several adventures as if it had a gamemaster narrating classic RPG campaigns from which the player will benefit from new content, in addition to all this, it will have season passes COMPLETELY FREE.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>No micro-transactions! No cash shop!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The fights are intense and strategic and any mistake can make you lose.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/c37d751fa7192654eaf9b359c3f1113d.poster.avif?t=1731027657\" width=600 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/c37d751fa7192654eaf9b359c3f1113d.webm?t=1731027657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/c37d751fa7192654eaf9b359c3f1113d.mp4?t=1731027657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Players can choose from a variety of vocations and abilities, each with their own strengths and weaknesses!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/26762365c533b990af55e27ed83007e3.poster.avif?t=1731027657\" width=600 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/26762365c533b990af55e27ed83007e3.webm?t=1731027657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/26762365c533b990af55e27ed83007e3.mp4?t=1731027657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Players can summon allies who will help them face greater challenges and receive great rewards!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/fb3ad49dc7e3f0cbdf3dfe650c4387d5.poster.avif?t=1731027657\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/fb3ad49dc7e3f0cbdf3dfe650c4387d5.webm?t=1731027657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/fb3ad49dc7e3f0cbdf3dfe650c4387d5.mp4?t=1731027657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Players can join a guild and carry out special quests, evolving and receiving unique rewards to exchange for special items!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/ada1da6a7a817fdec98ea236780cf730.poster.avif?t=1731027657\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/ada1da6a7a817fdec98ea23